	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This spell is extremely useful in solo and duelling. It has a casting time on 1 sec so it is easy to time to get off. The stun sets you up to cast a spell with a longer casting time, or perhaps get the jump on your would-be-slayer and get to a zone.<BR>
It is even better in duelling with out a pet(and I would assume PvP). After you throw alot of mana into a duel, cast this to get the time to cast mes. Then sit down right in front of you opponent and meditate to get mana back to finish the duel=)<BR>
Against a warrior I once went from under half mana to full while my dot's slowly killed him during the mes's, and this spell makes the combo possible.<BR>
Just be careful when casting it around numerous enemies, it makes you very popular.<BR>
<BR>
Liminus Veldrin
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
